generator.misc

Class DataFileDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • generator.misc.DataFileDefinition

  • public class DataFileDefinition
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the information used to create a new text output file. It also holds a vector of DataFileItem which define what to output in the text file.
